title: James Murray (comedian)
summary: James Stephen "Murr" Murray (born May 1, 1976) is an American improvisational comedian and actor from New York. He is a member of The Tenderloins, a comedy troupe also consisting of Brian Quinn, Sal Vulcano, and formerly Joe Gatto. Along with the other members of The Tenderloins, he stars in the television series Impractical Jokers, which premiered December 15, 2011, on TruTV.
